      "content": "1\n00:00:00,080 --> 00:00:07,100\n(soft music)\n\n2\n00:00:07,220 --> 00:00:11,980\nEwan ko ba kung bakit type kita?\n\n3\n00:00:14,360 --> 00:00:17,220\n'Di ka naman gwapo\n\n4\n00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:26,100\nKahit malabo ang pagpili ko\n\n5\n00:00:27,320 --> 00:00:31,560\nT.L. ako sa 'yo\n\n6\n00:00:33,060 --> 00:00:37,900\nPana'y kantyaw ng mga utol ko\n\n7\n00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:45,860\nDehins ka daw bagay sa kagandahan ko\n\n8\n00:00:45,980 --> 00:00:52,560\nMalabo na ba raw ang mata ko\n\n9\n00:00:53,160 --> 00:00:56,600\nAt na-T.L. kita\n\n10\n00:00:57,960 --> 00:01:04,000\nKalyeng liku-liko ang takbo ng isip ko\n\n11\n00:01:04,720 --> 00:01:11,080\nSabi ng lolo, may toyo ang utak ko\n\n12\n00:01:11,220 --> 00:01:16,920\nSabi ng lola ay humanap ng iba\n\n13\n00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:20,560\nMay porma't mayaman\n\n14\n00:01:20,620 --> 00:01:25,120\nT.L., wala naman\n\n15\n00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:31,120\nEwan ko ba kung bakit type kita?\n\n16\n00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:36,320\n'Di ka naman gwapo\n\n17\n00:01:39,100 --> 00:01:45,100\nKahit malabo ang pagpili ko\n\n18\n00:01:46,300 --> 00:01:50,140\nT.L. ako sa 'yo\n\n19\n00:01:51,060 --> 00:01:57,780\nKalyeng liku-liko ang takbo ng isip ko\n\n20\n00:01:57,820 --> 00:02:04,220\nSabi ng lolo, may toyo ang utak ko\n\n21\n00:02:04,300 --> 00:02:09,758\nSabi ng lola ay humanap ng iba\n\n22\n00:02:10,460 --> 00:02:13,520\nMay porma't mayaman\n\n23\n00:02:13,700 --> 00:02:19,340\nT.L., wala naman\n\n24\n00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:24,180\nEwan ko ba kung bakit type kita?\n\n25\n00:02:26,540 --> 00:02:30,100\n'Di ka naman gwapo\n\n26\n00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:38,120\nKahit malabo ang pagpili ko\n\n27\n00:02:39,380 --> 00:02:43,320\nT.L. ako sa 'yo\n\n28\n00:02:45,740 --> 00:02:50,080\nT.L. ako sa 'yo\n\n29\n00:02:50,240 --> 00:03:00,760\nIkaw ang true love ko\n"
